    public final class ParallelDeducer<I,T1,T2,T3,T4,T5,T6,T7,T8,T9,T10,O>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Deducer<I,O>
    The Class ParallelDeducer. This class describes the functionality of a Deducer which takes a Flux of inputs, parses them through a collection of deducers and subsequently combines them with the original data from which the deductions were derived.
